var book = {
	"name": "Lamentations",
	"numChapters": 5,
	"chapters": {
		"1": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">1 </span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20312A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20312A\"></sup>How lonely sits the citythat was full of people!How like <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20312B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20312B\"></sup>a widow has she become,she who was great among the nations!She who was <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20312C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20312C\"></sup>a princess among the provinceshas become <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20312D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20312D\"></sup>a slave.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20313E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20313E\"></sup>She weeps bitterly in the night,with tears on her cheeks;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20313F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20313F\"></sup>among all her loversshe has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20313G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20313G\"></sup>none to comfort her;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20313H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20313H\"></sup>all her friends have dealt treacherously with her;they have become her enemies.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20314I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20314I\"></sup>Judah has gone into exile because of afflictionand hard servitude;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20314J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20314J\"></sup>she dwells now among the nations,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20314K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20314K\"></sup>but finds no resting place;her pursuers have all overtaken herin the midst of her distress.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>The roads to Zion mourn,for none come to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20315L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20315L\"></sup>the festival;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20315M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20315M\"></sup>all her gates are desolate;her priests <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20315N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20315N\"></sup>groan;her virgins have been afflicted,and she herself suffers bitterly.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20316O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20316O\"></sup>Her foes have become the head;her <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20316P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20316P\"></sup>enemies prosper,because <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20316Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20316Q\"></sup>the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has afflicted her<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20316R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20316R\"></sup>for the multitude of her transgressions;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20316S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20316S\"></sup>her children have gone away,captives before the foe.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>From the daughter of Zionall her majesty has departed.Her princes have become like deer<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20317T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20317T\"></sup>that find no pasture;they fled without strengthbefore the pursuer.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Jerusalem remembersin the days of her affliction and wandering<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20318U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20318U\"></sup>all the precious thingsthat were hers from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20318V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20318V\"></sup>days of old.When her people fell into the hand of the foe,and there was none to help her,her foes gloated over her;they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20318W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20318W\"></sup>mocked at her downfall.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20319X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20319X\"></sup>Jerusalem sinned grievously;therefore she became filthy;all who honored her despise her,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20319Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20319Y\"></sup>for they have seen her nakedness;she herself <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20319Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20319Z\"></sup>groansand turns her face away.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Her uncleanness was <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20320AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20320AA\"></sup>in her skirts;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20320AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20320AB\"></sup>she took no thought of her future;therefore her fall is terrible;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20320AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20320AC\"></sup>she has no comforter.“O <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, behold my affliction,for the enemy has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20320AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20320AD\"></sup>triumphed!”",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>The enemy has stretched out his handsover all her <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20321AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20321AE\"></sup>precious things;for she has seen <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20321AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20321AF\"></sup>the nationsenter her sanctuary,those whom you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20321AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20321AG\"></sup>forbadeto enter your congregation.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>All her people <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20322AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20322AH\"></sup>groanas <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20322AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20322AI\"></sup>they search for bread;they trade their <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20322AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20322AJ\"></sup>treasures for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20322AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20322AK\"></sup>foodto revive their strength.“Look, O <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, and see,for I am despised.”",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>“Is it nothing to you, all <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20323AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20323AL\"></sup>you who pass by?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20323AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20323AM\"></sup>Look and seeif there is any sorrow like my sorrow,which was brought upon me,which <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20323AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20323AN\"></sup>the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> inflictedon <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20323AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20323AO\"></sup>the day of his fierce anger.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>“From on high he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20324AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20324AP\"></sup>sent fire;into my bones he made it descend;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20324AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20324AQ\"></sup>he spread a net for my feet;he turned me back;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20324AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20324AR\"></sup>he has left me stunned,faint all the day long.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>“My transgressions were bound into <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20325AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20325AS\"></sup>a yoke;by his hand they were fastened together;they were set upon my neck;he caused my strength to fail;the Lord gave me into the handsof those whom I cannot withstand.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>“The Lord rejectedall my mighty men in my midst;he summoned an assembly against meto crush my young men;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20326AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20326AT\"></sup>the Lord has trodden as in a winepressthe virgin daughter of Judah.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>“For these things <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20327AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20327AU\"></sup>I weep;my eyes flow with tears;for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20327AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20327AV\"></sup>a comforter is far from me,one to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20327AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20327AW\"></sup>revive my spirit;my children are desolate,for the enemy has prevailed.”",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20328AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20328AX\"></sup>Zion stretches out her hands,but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20328AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20328AY\"></sup>there is none to comfort her;the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has commanded against Jacobthat his neighbors should be his foes;Jerusalem has becomea filthy thing among them.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20329AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20329AZ\"></sup>“The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> is in the right,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20329BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20329BA\"></sup>for I have rebelled against his word;but hear, all you peoples,and see my suffering;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20329BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20329BB\"></sup>my young women and my young menhave gone into captivity.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>“I called to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20330BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20330BC\"></sup>my lovers,but they deceived me;my priests and eldersperished in the city,while <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20330BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20330BD\"></sup>they sought foodto revive their strength.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>“Look, O <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, for I am in distress;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20331BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20331BE\"></sup>my stomach churns;my heart is wrung within me,because I have been very rebellious.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20331BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20331BF\"></sup>In the street the sword bereaves;in the house it is like death.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>“They heard <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20332BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20332BG\"></sup>my groaning,yet <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20332BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20332BH\"></sup>there is no one to comfort me.All my enemies have heard of my trouble;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20332BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20332BI\"></sup>they are glad that you have done it.You have brought the day you announced;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20332BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20332BJ\"></sup>now let them be as I am.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20333BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20333BK\"></sup>“Let all their evildoing come before you,and deal with themas <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20333BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20333BL\"></sup>you have dealt with mebecause of all my transgressions;for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20333BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20333BM\"></sup>my groans are many,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20333BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20333BN\"></sup>my heart is faint.”"
		},
		"2": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">2 </span>How the Lord in his angerhas set the daughter of Zion <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20334A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20334A\"></sup>under a cloud!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20334B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20334B\"></sup>He has cast down from heaven to earththe splendor of Israel;he has not remembered <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20334C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20334C\"></sup>his footstoolin the day of his anger.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>The Lord <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20335D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20335D\"></sup>has swallowed up <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20335E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20335E\"></sup>without mercyall the habitations of Jacob;in his wrath <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20335F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20335F\"></sup>he has broken downthe strongholds of the daughter of Judah;he has brought <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20335G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20335G\"></sup>down to the ground <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20335H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20335H\"></sup>in dishonorthe kingdom <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20335I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20335I\"></sup>and its rulers.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>He has cut down in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20336J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20336J\"></sup>fierce angerall <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20336K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20336K\"></sup>the might of Israel;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20336L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20336L\"></sup>he has withdrawn from them his right handin the face of the enemy;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20336M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20336M\"></sup>he has burned like a flaming fire in Jacob,consuming all around.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20337N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20337N\"></sup>He has bent his bow like an enemy,with his right hand set <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20337O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20337O\"></sup>like a foe;and he has killed all who were delightful in our eyesin the tent of the daughter of Zion;he has poured out his fury like fire.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20338P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20338P\"></sup>The Lord has become like an enemy;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20338Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20338Q\"></sup>he has swallowed up Israel;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20338R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20338R\"></sup>he has swallowed up all its palaces;he has laid in ruins its strongholds,and he has multiplied in the daughter of Judah<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20338S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20338S\"></sup>mourning and lamentation.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>He has laid waste his booth like a garden,laid in ruins <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20339T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20339T\"></sup>his meeting place;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20339U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20339U\"></sup>the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has made Zion forgetfestival and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20339V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20339V\"></sup>Sabbath,and in his fierce indignation has spurned king and priest.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20340W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20340W\"></sup>The Lord has scorned his altar,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20340X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20340X\"></sup>disowned his sanctuary;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20340Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20340Y\"></sup>he has delivered into the hand of the enemythe walls of her palaces;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20340Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20340Z\"></sup>they raised a clamor in the house of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>as on the day of festival.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20341AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20341AA\"></sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> determined to lay in ruins<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20341AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20341AB\"></sup>the wall of the daughter of Zion;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20341AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20341AC\"></sup>he stretched out the measuring line;he did not restrain his hand from destroying;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20341AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20341AD\"></sup>he caused rampart and wall to lament;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20341AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20341AE\"></sup>they languished together.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Her gates have sunk into the ground;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20342AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20342AF\"></sup>he has ruined <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20342AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20342AG\"></sup>and broken her bars;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20342AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20342AH\"></sup>her king and princes are among the nations;the law is no more,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20342AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20342AI\"></sup>her prophets findno vision from the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>The elders of the daughter of Zion<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20343AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20343AJ\"></sup>sit on the ground <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20343AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20343AK\"></sup>in silence;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20343AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20343AL\"></sup>they have thrown dust on their headsand <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20343AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20343AM\"></sup>put on sackcloth;the young women of Jerusalemhave bowed their heads to the ground.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20344AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20344AN\"></sup>My eyes are spent with weeping;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20344AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20344AO\"></sup>my stomach churns;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20344AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20344AP\"></sup>my bile is poured out to the ground<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20344AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20344AQ\"></sup>because of the destruction of the daughter of my people,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20344AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20344AR\"></sup>because infants and babies <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20344AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20344AS\"></sup>faintin the streets of the city.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>They cry to their mothers,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20345AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20345AT\"></sup>“Where is bread and wine?”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20345AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20345AU\"></sup>as they faint like a wounded manin the streets of the city,as their life is poured outon their mothers' bosom.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>What can I say for you, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20346AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20346AV\"></sup>to what compare you,O daughter of Jerusalem?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20346AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20346AW\"></sup>What can I liken to you, that I may comfort you,O virgin daughter of Zion?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20346AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20346AX\"></sup>For your ruin is vast as the sea;who can heal you?",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20347AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20347AY\"></sup>Your prophets have seen for youfalse and deceptive visions;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20347AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20347AZ\"></sup>they have not exposed your iniquityto <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20347BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20347BA\"></sup>restore your fortunes,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20347BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20347BB\"></sup>but have seen for you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20347BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20347BC\"></sup>oraclesthat are false and misleading.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>All who pass along the wayclap their hands at you;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20348BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20348BD\"></sup>they hiss and wag their headsat the daughter of Jerusalem:“Is this the city that was called<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20348BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20348BE\"></sup>the perfection of beauty,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20348BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20348BF\"></sup>the joy of all the earth?”",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20349BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20349BG\"></sup>All your enemiesrail against you;they hiss, they gnash their teeth,they cry: “We <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20349BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20349BH\"></sup>have swallowed her!Ah, this is the day we longed for;now we have it; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20349BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20349BI\"></sup>we see it!”",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has done what he purposed;he has carried out <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20350BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20350BJ\"></sup>his word,which he commanded <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20350BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20350BK\"></sup>long ago;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20350BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20350BL\"></sup>he has thrown down <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20350BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20350BM\"></sup>without pity;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20350BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20350BN\"></sup>he has made the enemy rejoice over youand exalted the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20350BO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BO&quot;&gt;BO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20350BO\"></sup>might of your foes.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>Their heart cried to the Lord.O <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20351BP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BP&quot;&gt;BP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20351BP\"></sup>wall of the daughter of Zion,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20351BQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BQ&quot;&gt;BQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20351BQ\"></sup>let tears stream down like a torrent<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20351BR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BR&quot;&gt;BR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20351BR\"></sup>day and night!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20351BS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BS&quot;&gt;BS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20351BS\"></sup>Give yourself no rest,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20351BT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BT&quot;&gt;BT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20351BT\"></sup>your eyes no respite!",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>“Arise, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20352BU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BU&quot;&gt;BU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20352BU\"></sup>cry out in the night,at the beginning of the night watches!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20352BV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BV&quot;&gt;BV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20352BV\"></sup>Pour out your heart like waterbefore the presence of the Lord!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20352BW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BW&quot;&gt;BW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20352BW\"></sup>Lift your hands to himfor the lives of your children,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20352BX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BX&quot;&gt;BX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20352BX\"></sup>who faint for hungerat the head of every street.”",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>Look, O <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, and see!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20353BY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BY&quot;&gt;BY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20353BY\"></sup>With whom have you dealt thus?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20353BZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BZ&quot;&gt;BZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20353BZ\"></sup>Should women eat the fruit of their womb,the children of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20353CA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CA&quot;&gt;CA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20353CA\"></sup>their tender care?Should <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20353CB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CB&quot;&gt;CB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20353CB\"></sup>priest and prophet be killedin the sanctuary of the Lord?",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>In the dust of the streets<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20354CC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CC&quot;&gt;CC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20354CC\"></sup>lie the young and the old;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20354CD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CD&quot;&gt;CD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20354CD\"></sup>my young women and my young menhave fallen by the sword;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20354CE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CE&quot;&gt;CE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20354CE\"></sup>you have killed them in the day of your anger,slaughtering <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20354CF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CF&quot;&gt;CF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20354CF\"></sup>without pity.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>You summoned as if to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20355CG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CG&quot;&gt;CG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20355CG\"></sup>a festival day<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20355CH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CH&quot;&gt;CH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20355CH\"></sup>my terrors on every side,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20355CI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CI&quot;&gt;CI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20355CI\"></sup>and on the day of the anger of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>no one escaped or survived;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20355CJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CJ&quot;&gt;CJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20355CJ\"></sup>those whom I held and raisedmy enemy destroyed."
		},
		"3": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">3 </span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20356A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20356A\"></sup>I am the man who has seen afflictionunder the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20356B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20356B\"></sup>rod of his wrath;",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>he has driven and brought me<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20357C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20357C\"></sup>into darkness without any light;",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>surely against me he turns his handagain and again the whole day long.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>He has made my flesh and my skin waste away;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20359D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20359D\"></sup>he has broken my bones;",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20360E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20360E\"></sup>he has besieged and enveloped mewith <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20360F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20360F\"></sup>bitterness and tribulation;",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20361G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20361G\"></sup>he has made me dwell in darknesslike the dead of long ago.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20362H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20362H\"></sup>He has walled me about so that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20362I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20362I\"></sup>I cannot escape;he has made my chains heavy;",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>though <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20363J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20363J\"></sup>I call and cry for help,he shuts out my prayer;",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20364K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20364K\"></sup>he has blocked my ways with blocks of stones;he has made my paths crooked.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20365L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20365L\"></sup>He is a bear lying in wait for me,a lion in hiding;",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20366M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20366M\"></sup>he turned aside my steps and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20366N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20366N\"></sup>tore me to pieces;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20366O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20366O\"></sup>he has made me desolate;",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20367P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20367P\"></sup>he bent his bow <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20367Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20367Q\"></sup>and set meas a target for his arrow.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>He drove into my kidneys<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20368R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20368R\"></sup>the arrows of his quiver;",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20369S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20369S\"></sup>I have become the laughingstock of all peoples,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20369T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20369T\"></sup>the object of their taunts all day long.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20370U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20370U\"></sup>He has filled me with bitterness;he has sated me with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20370V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20370V\"></sup>wormwood.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20371W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20371W\"></sup>He has made my teeth grind on gravel,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20371X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20371X\"></sup>made me cower in ashes;",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>my soul is bereft of peace;I have forgotten what happiness is;",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20373Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20373Y\"></sup>so I say, “My endurance has perished;so has my hope from the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.”",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20374Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20374Z\"></sup>Remember my affliction and my wanderings,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20374AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20374AA\"></sup>the wormwood and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20374AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20374AB\"></sup>the gall!",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>My soul continually remembers it<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20375AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20375AC\"></sup>and is bowed down within me.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>But this I call to mind,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20376AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20376AD\"></sup>therefore I have hope:",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20377AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20377AE\"></sup>The steadfast love of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> never ceases;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20377AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20377AF\"></sup>his mercies never come to an end;",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>they are new <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20378AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20378AG\"></sup>every morning;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20378AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20378AH\"></sup>great is your faithfulness.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20379AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20379AI\"></sup>“The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> is my portion,” says my soul,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20379AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20379AJ\"></sup>“therefore I will hope in him.”",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> is good to those who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20380AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20380AK\"></sup>wait for him,to the soul who seeks him.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20381AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20381AL\"></sup>It is good that one should wait quietlyfor the salvation of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20382AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20382AM\"></sup>It is good for a man that he bearthe yoke <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20382AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20382AN\"></sup>in his youth.",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>Let him <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20383AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20383AO\"></sup>sit alone in silencewhen it is laid on him;",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20384AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20384AP\"></sup>let him put his mouth in the dust—there may yet be hope;",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20385AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20385AQ\"></sup>let him give his cheek to the one who strikes,and let him be filled with insults.",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20386AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20386AR\"></sup>For the Lord will notcast off forever,",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>but, though he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20387AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20387AS\"></sup>cause grief, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20387AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20387AT\"></sup>he will have compassion<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20387AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20387AU\"></sup>according to the abundance of his steadfast love;",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20388AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20388AV\"></sup>for he does not afflict from his heartor <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20388AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20388AW\"></sup>grieve the children of men.",
			"34": "<sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup>To crush underfootall <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20389AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20389AX\"></sup>the prisoners of the earth,",
			"35": "<sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20390AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20390AY\"></sup>to deny a man justicein the presence of the Most High,",
			"36": "<sup class=\"versenum\">36 </sup>to subvert a man in his lawsuit,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20391AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20391AZ\"></sup>the Lord does not approve.",
			"37": "<sup class=\"versenum\">37 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20392BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20392BA\"></sup>Who has spoken and it came to pass,unless the Lord has commanded it?",
			"38": "<sup class=\"versenum\">38 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20393BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20393BB\"></sup>Is it not from the mouth of the Most Highthat good and bad come?",
			"39": "<sup class=\"versenum\">39 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20394BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20394BC\"></sup>Why should a living man complain,a man, about the punishment of his sins?",
			"40": "<sup class=\"versenum\">40 </sup>Let us test and examine our ways,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20395BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20395BD\"></sup>and return to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>!",
			"41": "<sup class=\"versenum\">41 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20396BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20396BE\"></sup>Let us lift up our hearts and handsto God in heaven:",
			"42": "<sup class=\"versenum\">42 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20397BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20397BF\"></sup>“We have transgressed and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20397BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20397BG\"></sup>rebelled,and you have not forgiven.",
			"43": "<sup class=\"versenum\">43 </sup>“You have wrapped yourself with anger and pursued us,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20398BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20398BH\"></sup>killing without pity;",
			"44": "<sup class=\"versenum\">44 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20399BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20399BI\"></sup>you have wrapped yourself with a cloudso that no prayer can pass through.",
			"45": "<sup class=\"versenum\">45 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20400BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20400BJ\"></sup>You have made us scum and garbageamong the peoples.",
			"46": "<sup class=\"versenum\">46 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20401BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20401BK\"></sup>“All our enemiesopen their mouths against us;",
			"47": "<sup class=\"versenum\">47 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20402BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20402BL\"></sup>panic and pitfall have come upon us,devastation and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20402BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20402BM\"></sup>destruction;",
			"48": "<sup class=\"versenum\">48 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20403BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20403BN\"></sup>my eyes flow with rivers of tearsbecause of the destruction of the daughter of my people.",
			"49": "<sup class=\"versenum\">49 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20404BO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BO&quot;&gt;BO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20404BO\"></sup>“My eyes will flow without ceasing,without respite,",
			"50": "<sup class=\"versenum\">50 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20405BP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BP&quot;&gt;BP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20405BP\"></sup>until the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> from heavenlooks down and sees;",
			"51": "<sup class=\"versenum\">51 </sup>my eyes cause me griefat the fate of all the daughters of my city.",
			"52": "<sup class=\"versenum\">52 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20407BQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BQ&quot;&gt;BQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20407BQ\"></sup>“I have been hunted <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20407BR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BR&quot;&gt;BR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20407BR\"></sup>like a birdby those who were my enemies <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20407BS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BS&quot;&gt;BS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20407BS\"></sup>without cause;",
			"53": "<sup class=\"versenum\">53 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20408BT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BT&quot;&gt;BT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20408BT\"></sup>they flung me alive into the pit<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20408BU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BU&quot;&gt;BU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20408BU\"></sup>and cast stones on me;",
			"54": "<sup class=\"versenum\">54 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20409BV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BV&quot;&gt;BV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20409BV\"></sup>water closed over my head;I said, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20409BW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BW&quot;&gt;BW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20409BW\"></sup>‘I am lost.’",
			"55": "<sup class=\"versenum\">55 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20410BX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BX&quot;&gt;BX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20410BX\"></sup>“I called on your name, O <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,from the depths of the pit;",
			"56": "<sup class=\"versenum\">56 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20411BY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BY&quot;&gt;BY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20411BY\"></sup>you heard my plea, ‘Do not closeyour ear to my cry for help!’",
			"57": "<sup class=\"versenum\">57 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20412BZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BZ&quot;&gt;BZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20412BZ\"></sup>You came near when I called on you;you said, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20412CA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CA&quot;&gt;CA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20412CA\"></sup>‘Do not fear!’",
			"58": "<sup class=\"versenum\">58 </sup>“You have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20413CB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CB&quot;&gt;CB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20413CB\"></sup>taken up my cause, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20413CC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CC&quot;&gt;CC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20413CC\"></sup>O Lord;you have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20413CD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CD&quot;&gt;CD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20413CD\"></sup>redeemed my life.",
			"59": "<sup class=\"versenum\">59 </sup>You have seen the wrong done to me, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20414CE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CE&quot;&gt;CE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20414CE\"></sup>O <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>;judge my cause.",
			"60": "<sup class=\"versenum\">60 </sup>You have seen all their vengeance,all <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20415CF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CF&quot;&gt;CF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20415CF\"></sup>their plots against me.",
			"61": "<sup class=\"versenum\">61 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20416CG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CG&quot;&gt;CG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20416CG\"></sup>“You have heard their taunts, O <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,all <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20416CH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CH&quot;&gt;CH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20416CH\"></sup>their plots against me.",
			"62": "<sup class=\"versenum\">62 </sup>The lips and thoughts <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20417CI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CI&quot;&gt;CI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20417CI\"></sup>of my assailantsare against me all the day long.",
			"63": "<sup class=\"versenum\">63 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20418CJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CJ&quot;&gt;CJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20418CJ\"></sup>Behold their sitting and their rising;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20418CK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CK&quot;&gt;CK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20418CK\"></sup>I am the object of their taunts.",
			"64": "<sup class=\"versenum\">64 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20419CL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CL&quot;&gt;CL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20419CL\"></sup>“You will repay them, O <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20419CM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CM&quot;&gt;CM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20419CM\"></sup>according to the work of their hands.",
			"65": "<sup class=\"versenum\">65 </sup>You will give them dullness of heart;your curse will be on them.",
			"66": "<sup class=\"versenum\">66 </sup>You will pursue them in anger and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20421CN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CN&quot;&gt;CN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20421CN\"></sup>destroy themfrom under <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20421CO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CO&quot;&gt;CO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20421CO\"></sup>your heavens, O <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.”"
		},
		"4": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">4 </span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20422A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20422A\"></sup>How the gold has grown dim,how the pure gold is changed!The holy stones lie scattered<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20422B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20422B\"></sup>at the head of every street.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>The precious sons of Zion,worth their weight in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20423C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20423C\"></sup>fine gold,how they are regarded as <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20423D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20423D\"></sup>earthen pots,the work of a potter's hands!",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Even jackals offer the breast;they nurse their young;but the daughter of my people has become cruel,like the ostriches in the wilderness.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>The tongue of the nursing infant <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20425E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20425E\"></sup>sticksto the roof of its mouth for thirst;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20425F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20425F\"></sup>the children beg for food,but no one gives to them.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Those who once feasted on delicaciesperish in the streets;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20426G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20426G\"></sup>those who were brought up in purpleembrace ash heaps.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20427H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20427H\"></sup>For the chastisement of the daughter of my people has been greaterthan the punishment of Sodom,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20427I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20427I\"></sup>which was overthrown in a moment,and no hands were wrung for her.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Her princes were purer than snow,whiter than milk;their bodies were more ruddy than coral,the beauty of their form was like sapphire.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20429J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20429J\"></sup>Now their face is blacker than soot;they are not recognized in the streets;their skin has shriveled on their bones;it has become as dry as wood.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Happier were the victims of the swordthan the victims of hunger,who wasted away, piercedby lack of the fruits of the field.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20431K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20431K\"></sup>The hands of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20431L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20431L\"></sup>compassionate women<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20431M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20431M\"></sup>have boiled their own children;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20431N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20431N\"></sup>they became their foodduring the destruction of the daughter of my people.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20432O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20432O\"></sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> gave full vent to his wrath;he poured out his hot anger,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20432P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20432P\"></sup>he kindled a fire in Zionthat consumed its foundations.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20433Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20433Q\"></sup>The kings of the earth did not believe,nor any of the inhabitants of the world,that foe or enemy could enterthe gates of Jerusalem.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>This was for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20434R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20434R\"></sup>the sins of her prophetsand <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20434S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20434S\"></sup>the iniquities of her priests,who shed in the midst of herthe blood of the righteous.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20435T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20435T\"></sup>They wandered, blind, through the streets;they were so defiled with blood<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20435U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20435U\"></sup>that no one was able to touchtheir garments.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>“Away! <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20436V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20436V\"></sup>Unclean!” people cried at them.“Away! Away! Do not touch!”So they became fugitives and wanderers;people said among the nations,“They shall stay with us no longer.”",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20437W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20437W\"></sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> himself has scattered them;he will regard them no more;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20437X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20437X\"></sup>no honor was shown to the priests,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20437Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20437Y\"></sup>no favor to the elders.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20438Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20438Z\"></sup>Our eyes failed, ever watching<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20438AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20438AA\"></sup>vainly for help;in our watching we watchedfor <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20438AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20438AB\"></sup>a nation which could not save.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20439AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20439AC\"></sup>They dogged our stepsso that we could not walk in our streets;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20439AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20439AD\"></sup>our end drew near; our days were numbered,for our end had come.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>Our pursuers were <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20440AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20440AE\"></sup>swifterthan the eagles in the heavens;they chased us on the mountains;they lay in wait for us in the wilderness.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20441AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20441AF\"></sup>The breath of our nostrils, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20441AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20441AG\"></sup>the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>'s anointed,was captured <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20441AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20441AH\"></sup>in their pits,of whom we said, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20441AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20441AI\"></sup>“Under his shadowwe shall live among the nations.”",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20442AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20442AJ\"></sup>Rejoice and be glad, O daughter of Edom,you who dwell in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20442AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20442AK\"></sup>the land of Uz;but to you also <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20442AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20442AL\"></sup>the cup shall pass;you shall become drunk and strip yourself bare.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20443AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20443AM\"></sup>The punishment of your iniquity, O daughter of Zion, is accomplished;he will keep you in exile no longer;but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20443AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20443AN\"></sup>your iniquity, O daughter of Edom, he will punish;he will uncover your sins."
		},
		"5": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">5 </span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20444A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20444A\"></sup>Remember, O <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, what has befallen us;look, and see <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20444B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20444B\"></sup>our disgrace!",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20445C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20445C\"></sup>Our inheritance has been turned over to strangers,our homes to foreigners.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>We have become orphans, fatherless;our mothers are like widows.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>We must pay for the water we drink;the wood we get must be bought.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20448D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20448D\"></sup>Our pursuers are at our necks;we are weary; we are given no rest.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>We have given the hand to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20449E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20449E\"></sup>Egypt, and to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20449F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20449F\"></sup>Assyria,to get bread enough.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Our fathers sinned, and are no more;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20450G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20450G\"></sup>and we bear their iniquities.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20451H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20451H\"></sup>Slaves rule over us;there is none to deliver us from their hand.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20452I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20452I\"></sup>We get our bread at the peril of our lives,because of the sword in the wilderness.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20453J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20453J\"></sup>Our skin is hot as an ovenwith <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20453K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20453K\"></sup>the burning heat of famine.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Women are raped in Zion,young women in the towns of Judah.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20455L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20455L\"></sup>Princes are hung up by their hands;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20455M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20455M\"></sup>no respect is shown to the elders.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Young men are compelled to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20456N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20456N\"></sup>grind at the mill,and boys stagger <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20456O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20456O\"></sup>under loads of wood.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20457P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20457P\"></sup>The old men have left the city gate,the young men <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20457Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20457Q\"></sup>their music.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20458R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20458R\"></sup>The joy of our hearts has ceased;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20458S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20458S\"></sup>our dancing has been turned to mourning.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20459T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20459T\"></sup>The crown has fallen from our head;woe to us, for we have sinned!",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>For this <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20460U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20460U\"></sup>our heart has become sick,for these things <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20460V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20460V\"></sup>our eyes have grown dim,",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>for Mount Zion which lies desolate;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20461W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20461W\"></sup>jackals prowl over it.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20462X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20462X\"></sup>But you, O <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, reign forever;your throne endures to all generations.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20463Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20463Y\"></sup>Why do you forget us forever,why do you forsake us for so many days?",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20464Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20464Z\"></sup>Restore us to yourself, O <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, that we may be restored!Renew our days as of old—",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-20465AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-20465AA\"></sup>unless you have utterly rejected us,and you remain exceedingly angry with us."
		}
	}
};
module.exports = book;